  <data name="welcomeDescLabel.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Welcome to the University Management System Administrative Console.

From this dashboard, you can perform primary operations across all sectors:
- Manage Student and Instructor directories
- Configure Departments and Course listings
- Register student Enrollments
- Direct scheduling parameters
- Access reporting &amp; visual analytics</value>
